text: Osteopelta is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Osteopeltidae. ==Species== Species within the genus Osteopelta include: * Osteopelta ceticola Warén, 1989 * Osteopelta mirabilis Marshall, 1987 * Osteopelta praeceps B.A. Marshall, 1994 ==References== Category:Osteopeltidae
title: Osteopelta
